{"tid":2141933,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"內地研法定數碼貨幣 四大行正內部測試數碼賬戶","createTime":"2020-08-06T05:19:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T05:35:36.000Z","uid":73883,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"afa509ee4014c230940af1610ac7f649306e8f8d","tid":2141933,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:19:13.000Z","msg":"《21世紀經濟報道》引述知情人士報道，數間內地大行正在深圳等地大規模測試數碼賬戶應用，為推出數碼貨幣作準備，但仍在內部研發和測試階段，未有具體推出時間。<br />\n<br />\n周一人行表示，2020年下半年將積極研發法定數碼貨幣。數碼貨幣由中國人民銀行牽頭，各家銀行數月前已開始測試。目前部份大行內部員工已經開始使用數碼貨幣於轉賬、繳費等功能。報道指，內地四大行正內部測試數碼人民幣電子賬戶，但該手機應該程式（App）暫時還未能公開下載，而程式打開後會有身份編碼。<br />\n<br />\n人行數字貨幣研究所今年4月表示，數碼人民幣將先在深圳、蘇州、雄安、成都及未來的冬奧會場景進行內部測試。消息人士透露，註冊App需在四大行其中一家開立數碼賬戶，用戶可增值資金到賬戶，並可選擇網銀或綁卡增值等，類似中國銀聯的雲閃付App。預計數碼貨幣有增值、提款、轉賬、掃碼消費等功能，其中轉賬可透過手機號進行，並正在測試無網絡轉賬功能，與微信、支付寶等第三方支付類似，用戶可互相掃描QR Code支付。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200806/C2CHRW5OTFCSNMO2UXD6PRJMQE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200806%2FC2CHRW5OTFCSNMO2UXD6PRJMQE%2F&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F6b0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=d451566f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2F20200806%2FC2CHRW5OTFCSNMO2UXD6PRJMQE%2F&h=60a1d559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/finance/20200806/C2CHRW5OTFCSNMO2UXD6PRJMQE/</a>"},{"pid":"09398a30b44884597a04183e1665e67268504d73","tid":2141933,"uid":239345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:20:58.000Z","msg":"數碼貨幣之後會唔會走唔到資"},{"pid":"5ddcb06308bbe54641be14f3ed019bc0a73d7f2f","tid":2141933,"uid":66514,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:21:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=AocAYB7PSZg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAocAYB7PSZg&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2F6b0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=0bf653f1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=AocAYB7PSZg</a>"},{"pid":"c40705ccc91cf710823b13e9b7c019029dd32368","tid":2141933,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:21:24.000Z","msg":"....."},{"pid":"cf7e92306ed270b7e1b126aba8fef4676ac91b6d","tid":2141933,"uid":73883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"09398a30b44884597a04183e1665e67268504d73","tid":2141933,"uid":239345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:20:58.000Z","msg":"數碼貨幣之後會唔會走唔到資"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"伊朗應該會收掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddca357a050b9c0541adf8687e06ccad8fd2fbfc","tid":2141933,"uid":225798,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"大富翁幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fd34f5b85885abef72a14a35af5d5e186cda217","tid":2141933,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:28:04.000Z","msg":"數碼出糧"},{"pid":"fab99758902275544771c6bd9dcde289e05fd11d","tid":2141933,"uid":121672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T05:35:36.000Z","msg":"喺大陸銀行啲錢突然無晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}